author: Atomic Shrimp
description:
Today I am cooking with foraged common mallow, in collaboration with my friend Babatunde from Nigeria; this recipe is one that might challenge my palate, on account of the texture.

His video of this recipe may be found here: https://youtu.be/espKAGjt1LA

Join the Atomic Shrimp official Discord server for FREE early access to videos! - https://discord.gg/atomicshrimp
